title: Bug 109350: Output parameter not displayed in data set dialog.
description: The output parameter is not being displayed in the edit data set dialog.
OB: While on the query result page, no data is returned. The actual result is that the output parameter should be displayed in the edit data set dialog.
EB: The output parameter should be displayed in the edit data set dialog.
SR:
To reproduce the issue, follow these steps:
1. Call the stored procedure from the Oracle database.
2. Check the query result and verify that it has been stored in the output parameter as an object.
